    Add common CLI function to parse comma-separated list of IMEX channels

    Signed-off-by: Kevin Klues <kklues@nvidia.com>
---
 src/cli/cli.h    |  5 +++++
 src/cli/common.c | 53 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 58 insertions(+)

