commit a6e502a7bfed8d373ff902975a44a7eb24578bdf
Author: Kevin Klues <kklues@nvidia.com>
Date:   Wed Oct 6 22:04:21 2021 +0000

    Add new cgroup.c file to support both cgroupv1 and cgroupv2

    The code in this file calls out to Go code in nvcgo library via RPC. The code
    itself will only be compiled / linked in if the WITH_NVCGO make variable is set.
    When this make variable is not set, the old legacy cgroup code from
    cgroup_legacy.c will be included instead.

    At present, this will error out with a permission error when attempting to
    modify the device cgroups. A subsequent commit will patch things up to
    explicitly set the right permissions across the call to set the device rules.

    Signed-off-by: Kevin Klues <kklues@nvidia.com>
---
 Makefile            |   8 ++-
 src/cgroup.c        | 191 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/nvc_container.c |   4 +-
 src/nvc_rpc.x       |  24 +++++++
 4 files changed, 223 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

