    Add Jenkinsfile for internal CI

    This change adds a Jenkins file that mirrors the build pipeline as defined
    in the .gitlab-ci.yml file. The Jenkinsfile assumes that the K8s plugin
    for Jenkins is being used.

    Note:
    * The single architecture targets (based on ubuntu18.04) is defined as a
      set of parallel stages
    * The targets for building all architecutre targets is also defined as a
      set of parallel stages.
    * The "build all" targets currently only echo the make command that WOULD
      be exectued.

